<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ChainBloom Bank Garden</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/orange-juice');
        body {
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #dff7ff 0%, #eefeea 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Orange Juice', cursive;
            color: #2d7c60;
        }
        .container {
            border: 3px solid #7ad6a5;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
            width: min(520px, 90vw);
            padding: 28px;
            margin: 70px auto;
            border-radius: 26px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(45,124,96,.16);
        }
        h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.4; }
        .links { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin-top: 26px; }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background: #49b675;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .mini {
            margin-top: 18px;
            color: #517767;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div style="font-size:4rem;">🌱🏦✨</div>
        <h1>ChainBloom</h1>
        <p>A collectible virtual plant that lives in your account. Use your bank balance like a wallet to water, feed, and grow your NFT-style garden companion.</p>
        <div class="links">
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/signup">Signup</a>
        </div>
        <div class="mini">Your savings account powers every care action in the garden.</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
